title: Skype 4.0.0.176 (beta 3, light installer)
description:
Skype allows users to make telephone calls over the Internet. Calls to other users of the service and to free-of-charge numbers are free, while calls to other landlines and mobile phones can be made for a small fee. Additional features include instant messaging, file transfer and video conferencing.

How to install:

Can't be any easier. After downloading the torrent, just open the exe file and follow the instructions.
